{"tid":926203,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人嚴重低估左運動既好處","createTime":"2018-12-03T09:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T10:31:12.000Z","uid":123335,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"985f64138d44bf3f74f8b04947ecca3145866d93","tid":926203,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:27:52.000Z","msg":"減低患上心臟病、糖尿病、高血壓、 肥胖、膝關節炎...etc 等疾病風險<br />\n只不過係運動帶來既副作用<br />\n我根本唔Care <br />\n<br />\n運動真正既好處<br />\n除左運動後會令你心情大好，提升EQ <br />\n仲有會振奮精神，提升驚覺性，清醒度，加快大腦轉數<br />\n唔好睇少呢兩點<br />\n單單係提升EQ , <br />\n已經令你同其他人關係提升唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ；<br />\n而覺醒後既大腦，亦令你以高轉數既效率黎吸收知識及作出分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲以為運動係用黎減肥 keep fit 咁簡單？<br />\n真係嚴重低估晒運動既好處"},{"pid":"f37db50639a8e963b4af11edd9c480f7377d5547","tid":926203,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"做gym計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88212ed037421c29103382e1f03391a79f8f71fe","tid":926203,"uid":123335,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"f37db50639a8e963b4af11edd9c480f7377d5547","tid":926203,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"做gym計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:30:26.000Z","msg":"點會唔計 <br />\n但電莖就真心唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1578608fbaacdb5d4ac14911e226d8c0f344cc17","tid":926203,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"打飛機計唔計"},{"pid":"1794bc1e2025028b9de3ff360cc5e25f8aee2ea5","tid":926203,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"做運動要上癮先有用，上癮就會好似玩手機咁自動自覺做"},{"pid":"ca5649a3811209839712219528b4371dcbac6b6d","tid":926203,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dis